### 事项管理接口

@baseUrl = http://localhost

### 创建事项
POST {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "事项标题",
  "description": "事项描述",
  "spaceId": 1,
  "type": "task",
  "priority": "high",
  "status": "todo"
}

### 更新事项
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "更新后的标题",
  "description": "更新后的描述",
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### 删除事项
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 根据ID查询事项详情（包含扩展字段）
GET {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 分页查询事项
POST {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "spaceId": null,
  "type": "",
  "status": "",
  "priority": "",
  "assigneeId": null,
  "keyword": ""
}

### 搜索事项（支持事项单号和标题搜索）
GET {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue/search?keyword=测试
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

